; Regression test for issue #836: Account aliases should match account name components (BZ#836)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/836
;
; Account aliases currently only expand when the alias matches the FIRST component
; of an account name. They do NOT expand when the alias matches a middle component.
;
; Example: "alias Food=Healthy:Food"
;   - "Food:Groceries" -> expands to "Healthy:Food:Groceries" (first component, works)
;   - "Expenses:Food:Groceries" -> does NOT expand "Food" (middle component, broken)
;
; Issue requests that aliases should match ANY component of an account name.

alias Food=Healthy:Food

2024/01/01 Test first-component alias expansion
    Food:Groceries              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Test middle-component alias expansion
    Expenses:Food:Groceries    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
            $-150.00  Assets:Cash
             $100.00  Expenses:Food:Groceries
              $50.00  Healthy:Food:Groceries
--------------------
                   0
end test
